{% extends 'sbadmin.html.twig' %}
{# Ici on se pose la question de savoir si ma vue doit avoir l'apparence de mon site ou d'un back office (d'admin)#}
{% block title %}Liste des articles{% endblock %}
    
{% block body %}
    <main>
        <div class="container-fluid px-4">
        {#{{ dump(posts)}}#}
            <h1>
                Liste des articles
                <a href="{{ path('admin_post_add') }}" class="btn btn-primary">Ajouter</a>
            </h1>
            <div class="card-body">
                <table id="datatablesSimple">
                    <thead>
                        <tr>
                            <th>N°</th>
                            <th>Libellé</th>
                            <th>Categry Id</th>
                            <th>Titre de l'articles</th>
                            <th>Slug</th>
                            <th>Contenu</th>
                            <th>Image</th>
                            <th>Date de Création</th>
                            <th>Active</th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tfoot>
                        <tr>
                            <th>N°</th>
                            <th>Libellé</th>
                            <th>Category Id</th>
                            <th>Titre de l'articles</th>
                            <th>Slug</th>
                            <th>Contenu</th>
                            <th>Image</th>
                            <th>Date de Création</th>
                            <th>Active</th>
                        </tr>
                    </tfoot>
                    
                    <tbody>

                    {% for post in posts %}
                        <tr>
                            <td>{{ post.id }}</td>
                            <td>{{ post.user.id }}</td>
                            <td>{{ post.category.id }}</td>
                            <td>{{ post.title }}</td>
                            <td>{{ post.slug }}</td>
                            <td><a href="{{ path('admin_post_view', {slug: post.slug}) }}">{{ post.content | u.truncate(150, '...') | raw }}</a></td>
                            <td>{{ post.image | u.truncate(10, '...') | raw }} </td>
                            <td>{{ post.createdAt | date }}</td>
                            <td>{{ post.active }}</td>
                            <td><a href="{{ path('admin_post_update', {id: post.id}) }}" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm">Modifier</a>
                            </td>
                            <td><a href="{{ path('admin_post_delete', {id: post.id}) }}" class="btn btn-warning btn-sm" onclick="return confirm('Suppression ?')">Supprimer</a></td>
                            <td>
                            <a href="" class="btn btn-danger btn-sm modal-trigger" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#modalDelete" data-id="{{ post.id }}" data-title="{{ post.title }}">Supprimer</a>
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                    {% endfor %}

                    </tbody>
                </table>
            </div>
          
        </div>
    </main>
    <!-- Modal -->
        <div class="modal fade" id="modalDelete" tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="exampleModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
            <div class="modal-dialog">
                <div class="modal-content">
                <div class="modal-header">
                    <h5 class="modal-title" id="exampleModalLabel">Supprimer un article</h5>
                    <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-body">
                    ...
                </div>
                <div class="modal-footer">
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-bs-dismiss="modal">Annuler</button>
                    <a href="" class="btn btn-primary">Supprimer</a>
                </div>
                </div>
            </div>
    </div>
    <script> 
        window.onload = () => {
            let btdeletes = document.querySelectorAll(".modal-trigger")
            for(let btdelete of btdeletes) {
            
                btdelete.addEventListener("click", function(){
                    document.querySelector(".modal-footer a").href=`/admin/post/delete/${this.dataset.id}`
                    document.querySelector(".modal-body").innerText = `Etes-vous sûr de vouloir supprimer cet article : "${this.dataset.title}"`
                })
            }
        }
    </script>
{% endblock %}